parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door latch can cause the doors to unexpectedly open while driving, increasing the risk of accidents or ejection of occupants.
symptoms: The doors do not lock
the doors unexpectedly open while driving
the door latch does not engage properly
the door remains open even when attempted to be closed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The design of the A-pillar can create a blind spot, obstructing the driver's view and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Difficulty seeing obstacles or pedestrians on the right side of the vehicle
accidents or near-misses due to reduced visibility.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic 911 system can lead to a delay in emergency response in the event of an accident, potentially putting the occupants' lives at risk.
symptoms: The automatic 911 system is no longer functional
and the vehicle is unable to send emergency calls in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door latch can cause the door to open while driving, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The driver door will not latch and stay shut
even when the vehicle is in motion
and there are no warning lights or indicators.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden explosion of the sunroof can cause injuries, damage to the vehicle, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: The sunroof suddenly explodes outward while driving
with no prior warning or indication of a problem.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden tire failure can lead to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Tire blowout or explosion
sudden loss of air pressure
vibration or shaking while driving
loud noise or bang while driving
loss of control or difficulty steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Repeated instances of tire failure can erode trust in the tire brand and lead to a loss of confidence in the safety of the vehicle, potentially causing drivers to avoid driving or limit their use of the vehicle.
symptoms: Fear or anxiety while driving due to tire reliability concerns
avoidance of highway driving or long trips
reduced vehicle usage.
